<div class="container">
  <div class="row text-center">
    <div clas="col-xs-12">
      <p>Dear <%= @reservation[:customer_first_name], %></p>
      <p>Thank you for your recent PawBookings.com reservation.</p>
      <p>Below is your Kennel Reservation details. Please review the following information for accuracy, and note the details contained in the IMPORTANT INFORMATION section below. If you have any questions, please email reservations@pawbookings.com immediately. Please put your Reservation Confirmation Number is the subject line of the email.</p>
      <p><strong>Reservation-ID: </strong><%= @reservation[:id] %></p>
      <p><strong>First Name: </strong><%= @reservation[:customer_first_name] %></p>
      <p><strong>Last Name: </strong><%= @reservation[:customer_last_name] %></p>
      <p><strong>Email: </strong><%= @reservation[:customer_email] %></p>
      <p><strong>Phone: </strong><%= @reservation[:customer_phone] %></p>
      <p><strong>Check-In Date: </strong><%= @reservation[:check_in_date] %></p>
      <p><strong>Check-Out Date: </strong><%= @reservation[:check_out_date] %></p>
      <p><strong>Confirmation-ID: </strong><%= @reservation[:transID] %></p>
      <p><strong>Total-Price: </strong><%= @total_price %></p>

      <h3 class="default_green_color">Pets:</h3>
      <% JSON.parse(@reservation[:pet_ids]).each do |pet_id| %>
        <% pet = Pet.find(pet_id) %>
        <p><strong>Name: </strong><%= pet[:name] %></p>
        <p><strong>Cat or Dog: </strong><%= pet[:cat_or_dog] %></p>
        <p><strong>Breed: </strong><%= pet[:breed] %></p>
        <p><strong>Weight: </strong><%= pet[:weight] %></p>
        <p><strong>Vaccinations: </strong><%= pet[:vaccinations] %></p>
        <p><strong>Spay or Neutered: </strong><%= pet[:spay_or_neutered] %></p>
        <p><strong>Special instructions: </strong><%= pet[:special_instructions] %></p>
      <% end %>

      <h3 class="default_green_color">Room Details:</h3>
      <% JSON.parse(@reservation[:room_details]).each do |key, val| %>
        <p><strong><%= "•#{key}- $#{val}" %></strong></p>
      <% end %>

      <h3 class="default_green_color">Amenity Details</h3>
      <% if @reservation[:amenity_details].nil? %>
        <p><strong>•No Amenities Chosen.</strong></p>
      <% else %>
        <% JSON.parse(@reservation[:amenity_details]).each do |title, description, price, quantity| %>
          <p><strong><%= title %></strong></p>
          <p><strong><%= description %></strong></p>
          <p><strong><%= "$#{price} x #{quantity}" %></strong></p>
          <br />
          <br />
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
      <div class="res_email_special_information">
        <p>You will be receiving a reminder email to upload the vaccination documents for your pet(s). Remember! It is extremely important that proof of vaccinations are uploaded to your account. Failure to provide proof of vaccinations may void your reservation.</p>
        <p>Please review the Change/Cancellation/Refund Policy included below. If you need to make changes to your reservation, please email reservations@pawbookings.com or call us at 1-844- 944-3333.</p>
        <p>Thank you again for choosing PawBookings.com to reserve your pet’s holiday!</p>
        <p>This email was sent to you by PawBookings.com. Please do not respond to this email. Please see this email and the other terms and conditions for this reservation for more details. © 2016. PawBookings.com, Inc. All Rights Reserved</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
